# Rule: Follow Angular Commit Convention

When committing, follow the Angular convention:

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>
<BLANK LINE>
<body - what changed>
<BLANK LINE>
<footer>
```

Reference: https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/22b96b9/CONTRIBUTING.md#-commit-message-guidelines